## 📌 What Are We Building?

A **Supply Chain Decision Engine** powered by Databricks Foundation Models.
The system processes orders and logistics data, then uses an LLM to generate smart supply chain decisions.

---

## 🏗️ Architecture

```mermaid
graph TD
    A[🖥️ Frontend UI] -->|HTTP| B[🐍 Python Backend]
    B -->|Databricks SDK| C[🔐 Auth Layer]
    C -->|WorkspaceClient| D[☁️ Databricks Workspace]
    D --> E[🤖 Foundation Model Endpoint\ndatabricks-claude-sonnet-4-5]

    style A fill:#4A90D9,color:#fff
    style B fill:#FF6B35,color:#fff
    style C fill:#F7C59F,color:#333
    style D fill:#FF3621,color:#fff
    style E fill:#1B1B1B,color:#fff
```

---

## 🔐 Authentication Flow

```mermaid
sequenceDiagram
    participant Dev as 💻 Developer
    participant CLI as Databricks CLI
    participant CFG as ~/.databrickscfg
    participant SDK as WorkspaceClient
    participant EP as Serving Endpoint

    Dev->>CLI: databricks auth login
    CLI->>CFG: Save credentials
    SDK->>CFG: Load credentials
    SDK->>EP: POST /serving-endpoints/{name}/invocations
    EP-->>SDK: LLM Response
```

