## 🗓️ Day-by-Day Log

<details>
<summary><b>📅 Day 1 — Bootstrap & First Connection</b></summary>

### 🎯 Goal
Get the project running locally and connect to Databricks for the first time.

### ✅ Wins
- Installed `uv` and `databricks-cli`
- Authenticated with Databricks workspace
- Called Foundation Model endpoint successfully

### ❌ Issues Hit

| # | Error | Fix |
|---|-------|-----|
| 1 | `uv` not recognized | Add `~/.local/bin` to PATH |
| 2 | `databricks` not recognized | Add Python Scripts folder to PATH |
| 3 | Auth failed | Use base URL only — no `/browse` or `/workspace` |
| 4 | `ENDPOINT_NOT_FOUND` | Use endpoint name, not model identifier |
| 5 | `404 Not Found` | Fix `.env` endpoint name |

### 💡 Key Lesson
> Endpoint name ≠ Model identifier.
> Always run `databricks serving-endpoints list` to confirm the correct name.

</details>

