## 🐛 Debug Playbook

```mermaid
flowchart TD
    START([❌ App Fails]) --> Q1{databricks\ncurrent-user me\nworks?}

    Q1 -->|No| FIX1[Run auth login\nwith base URL only]
    Q1 -->|Yes| Q2{Endpoint in\nserving-endpoints list?}

    Q2 -->|No| FIX2[Contact workspace admin]
    Q2 -->|Yes| Q3{.env has correct\nendpoint name?}

    Q3 -->|No| FIX3[Fix .env value]
    Q3 -->|Yes| FIX4[Check backend logs\nfor path errors]

    FIX1 --> END([✅ Resolved])
    FIX2 --> END
    FIX3 --> END
    FIX4 --> END

    style START fill:#ff5252,color:#fff
    style END fill:#69f0ae,color:#333
    style FIX1 fill:#fff9c4,color:#333
    style FIX2 fill:#fff9c4,color:#333
    style FIX3 fill:#fff9c4,color:#333
    style FIX4 fill:#fff9c4,color:#333
```

