## 🗂️ Issues Registry

| # | Error | Root Cause | Fix | Day |
|---|-------|-----------|-----|-----|
| 1 | `uv not found` | Not in PATH | Add `~/.local/bin` to PATH | Day 1 |
| 2 | `databricks not recognized` | Scripts not in PATH | Add Python Scripts to PATH | Day 1 |
| 3 | `cannot configure credentials` | Wrong auth URL | Use base workspace URL only | Day 1 |
| 4 | `ENDPOINT_NOT_FOUND` | Wrong name in `.env` | Use name from `serving-endpoints list` | Day 1 |
| 5 | `404 Not Found` | Model ID used instead of endpoint name | Fix `.env` | Day 1 |

